trans-unit.source: An inline-level flow content element which enables <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> elements (i.e. a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"></xref>) to be embedded (hosted) in flow content.
trans-unit.target: En infogad nivå flödet content-elementet som gör att <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> element (d.v.s. en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"> </xref>) som ska bäddas in (värd) i flödet innehåll.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> element (i.e. a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>) may be embedded directly in flow content by enclosing it in a InlineUIContainer (see example below).
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>element (d.v.s. en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>) kan vara inbäddat direkt i flödet innehåll inom en InlineUIContainer (se exemplet nedan).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: An InlineUIContainer may directly host no more than one <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> child.
trans-unit.target: En InlineUIContainer kan direkt värd för fler än en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>underordnade.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: However, the child element hosted by an InlineUIContainer may host children of its own.
trans-unit.target: Det underordnade elementet hos en InlineUIContainer kan dock vara värd för sin egen underordnade.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new, empty instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny, tom instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref> class, taking a specified <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> object as the initial contents of the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref> klass, tar en angiven <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> -objektet som det inledande innehållet i den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> object specifying the initial contents of the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> objekt som anger det inledande innehållet i den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref> class, taking a specified <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> object as the initial contents of the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref>, and a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TextPointer"></xref> specifying an insertion position for the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref> klass, tar en angiven <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> -objektet som det inledande innehållet i den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref>, och en <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TextPointer"> </xref> anger en infogning position för den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> object specifying the initial contents of the new <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> objekt som anger det inledande innehållet i den nya <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This parameter may be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, in which case no <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> is inserted.
trans-unit.target: Den här parametern kan vara <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, då ingen <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> infogas.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TextPointer"></xref> specifying an insertion position at which to insert the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref> element after it is created, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> for no automatic insertion.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TextPointer"> </xref> att ange en infogning position där du vill infoga den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref> elementet när den har skapats eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> för inte automatisk infogning.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> hosted by the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> som är värd för den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer> may directly host no more than one <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> child.
However, the child element hosted by an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer> may host children of its own.
trans-unit.target: Men det underordnade elementet som är värd för en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer>kan vara värd för sin egen underordnade.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer>

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlexaml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], wrapping a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> in an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer> is equivalent to setting that <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> as the value of the Child property.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlexaml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], wrapping en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>i en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer>ställer som motsvarar <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>som värde för egenskapen underordnade.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>
